cook a proper meal for you.

582
00:22:05,060 --> 00:22:06,380
Finally got the chance today.

583
00:22:06,620 --> 00:22:08,540
Just hope it suits your taste.

584
00:22:08,980 --> 00:22:09,860
It does!

585
00:22:10,580 --> 00:22:12,420
This chicken soup is really good.

586
00:22:14,020 --> 00:22:14,900
Let's skip this part.

587
00:22:15,220 --> 00:22:15,700
Skip it.

588
00:22:15,860 --> 00:22:16,220
Okay.

589
00:22:18,740 --> 00:22:19,980
This soup is delicious too.

590
00:22:22,980 --> 00:22:23,380
Let me try.

591
00:22:26,300 --> 00:22:26,980
By the way, Lexuan,

592
00:22:27,220 --> 00:22:29,180
Ms. Yan said the piece
for your Children's Day performance

593
00:22:29,300 --> 00:22:29,980
is quite challenging.

594
00:22:30,140 --> 00:22:31,260
You'll need to
put in more effort lately.

595
00:22:32,500 --> 00:22:32,900
I know.

596
00:22:33,380 --> 00:22:35,220
After this meal, I'm going
into serious practice mode.

597
00:22:36,060 --> 00:22:38,500
Should we ask Ms. Wen to tutor you?

598
00:22:39,540 --> 00:22:40,180
No problem.

599
00:22:40,700 --> 00:22:41,660
Lexuan and I work well together.

600
00:22:41,780 --> 00:22:42,580
It'll be fine, right?

601
00:22:42,780 --> 00:22:43,620
Absolutely.

602
00:22:44,620 --> 00:22:45,420
Oh, Rui,

603
00:22:45,460 --> 00:22:47,740
guess who I ran into at school today?

604
00:22:48,060 --> 00:22:48,380
Who?

605
00:22:49,300 --> 00:22:49,980
That friend of yours

606
00:22:51,060 --> 00:22:52,540
we met at the winery,

607
00:22:52,700 --> 00:22:53,220
Tan Siting.

608
00:22:56,620 --> 00:22:57,140
What a coincidence.

609
00:22:58,700 --> 00:22:59,340
She's now

610
00:22:59,340 --> 00:23:00,740
actually a ballet teacher

611
00:23:00,940 --> 00:23:01,820
at our training center.

612
00:23:02,300 --> 00:23:03,620
We're colleagues.

613
00:23:04,780 --> 00:23:05,300
Yes.

614
00:23:05,300 --> 00:23:06,460
She did mention

615
00:23:07,020 --> 00:23:09,380
she was coming back
to teach after retiring.

616
00:23:14,020 --> 00:23:15,020
This soup is really good.

617
00:23:17,820 --> 00:23:18,580
Could you get me...?

618
00:23:19,060 --> 00:23:19,660
Let me get you.

619
00:23:20,380 --> 00:23:20,900
Okay.

620
00:23:23,540 --> 00:23:24,060
Thanks, Mom.

621
00:23:24,820 --> 00:23:25,660
Let me get you some of that.

622
00:23:26,060 --> 00:23:26,460
Try it.

623
00:23:26,540 --> 00:23:26,740
Okay.

624
00:23:40,300 --> 00:23:41,340
You met her?

625
00:23:42,780 --> 00:23:43,220
Who?

626
00:23:49,860 --> 00:23:50,540
Tan Siting.

627
00:23:51,020 --> 00:23:51,940
Yes... I have seen her.

628
00:23:52,140 --> 00:23:53,140
Why didn't you tell me?

629
00:23:53,980 --> 00:23:55,540
Do I have to report everything to you?

630
00:23:56,060 --> 00:23:56,900
What did you talk about?

631
00:23:58,460 --> 00:24:00,380
Just ordinary greetings and small talk.

632
00:24:00,700 --> 00:24:01,580
No further contact?

633
00:24:03,220 --> 00:24:03,980
We just met once.

634
00:24:04,100 --> 00:24:05,580
Didn't exchange any contact information.

635
00:24:10,020 --> 00:24:10,820
It's strange.

636
00:24:12,500 --> 00:24:13,100
Of all places,

637
00:24:14,580 --> 00:24:15,900
she runs into you in this city.

638
00:24:16,500 --> 00:24:17,220
Of all places,

639
00:24:17,980 --> 00:24:19,380
she stumbles into your winery.

640
00:24:20,780 --> 00:24:21,380
And now

641
00:24:22,380 --> 00:24:23,820
she happens to be colleagues
with Peiyan.

642
00:24:26,020 --> 00:24:27,220
Don't you find that odd?

643
00:24:36,140 --> 00:24:37,060
What she does

644
00:24:37,060 --> 00:24:38,060
has nothing to do with me.

645
00:25:01,340 --> 00:25:02,020
Rui,

646
00:25:03,380 --> 00:25:04,260
don't forget.

647
00:25:05,020 --> 00:25:07,380
Back then, for the sake of her career,

648
00:25:07,780 --> 00:25:09,060
she didn't care about anything else.

649
00:25:09,740 --> 00:25:12,220
She left a letter and ran off to France.

650
00:25:14,980 --> 00:25:15,540
Lexuan

651
00:25:16,220 --> 00:25:17,860
was only this small back then.

652
00:25:18,860 --> 00:25:20,220
I worked myself to the bone.

653
00:25:20,580 --> 00:25:22,100
I ignored the company

654
00:25:22,460 --> 00:25:23,580
just to help you raise the child.

655
00:25:24,860 --> 00:25:27,100
We finally got our lives back on track.

656
00:25:28,740 --> 00:25:30,020
And now she suddenly reappears.

657
00:25:31,140 --> 00:25:32,020
What does she want?

658
00:25:33,100 --> 00:25:34,900
Does she want to ruin our lives again?

659
00:25:35,980 --> 00:25:36,340
Mom,

660
00:25:39,180 --> 00:25:39,940
it's impossible

661
00:25:41,420 --> 00:25:42,020
between her and me now.

662
00:25:44,140 --> 00:25:44,980
She's met Lexuan.

663
00:25:46,500 --> 00:25:47,020
But she

664
00:25:47,020 --> 00:25:47,980
showed no reaction to him.

665
00:25:48,380 --> 00:25:49,580
I've completely given up on her.

666
00:25:49,900 --> 00:25:51,140
She can no longer affect our family,

667
00:25:51,820 --> 00:25:52,700
and she certainly can't affect me.

668
00:25:57,220 --> 00:25:58,380
I'm relieved

669
00:25:59,820 --> 00:26:00,780
to hear you say that.

670
00:26:01,580 --> 00:26:03,060
I just wanted to remind you.

671
00:26:05,220 --> 00:26:06,260
Also,

672
00:26:09,060 --> 00:26:09,860
Peiyan

673
00:26:11,020 --> 00:26:14,220
is so good to you and Lexuan.

674
00:26:16,140 --> 00:26:16,940
We

675
00:26:17,900 --> 00:26:19,060
shouldn't fail her.

676
00:26:29,900 --> 00:26:30,460
You should head back.

677
00:26:47,580 --> 00:26:48,860
Head position.

678
00:26:48,860 --> 00:26:49,340
Hands.

679
00:26:51,020 --> 00:26:52,300
Watch your toes.

680
00:26:57,020 --> 00:26:57,540
Good.

681
00:26:58,940 --> 00:27:00,020
Move together.

682
00:27:03,100 --> 00:27:04,140
Very good.

683
00:27:08,140 --> 00:27:09,100
You did a great job
with the pirouette today.

684
00:27:09,300 --> 00:27:10,100
But still,

685
00:27:10,700 --> 00:27:12,060
pay attention to the emotion.

686
00:27:12,060 --> 00:27:13,580
You must feel the emotion
before you start dancing.

687
00:27:13,900 --> 00:27:14,260
Okay.

688
00:27:14,380 --> 00:27:15,180
Alright. You can go now.

689
00:27:15,340 --> 00:27:15,900
Practice well.

690
00:27:16,060 --> 00:27:16,860
Thank you, ma'am.

691
00:27:17,060 --> 00:27:17,820
Okay. Bye.

692
00:27:30,700 --> 00:27:31,500
Ms. Tan!

693
00:27:32,340 --> 00:27:33,660
Someone's at the door asking for you.

694
00:28:01,980 --> 00:28:03,180
You were doing just fine in Paris.

695
00:28:04,140 --> 00:28:05,820
Why come back all of a sudden?

696
00:28:06,820 --> 00:28:07,860
I came back because I wanted to.

697
00:28:08,500 --> 00:28:09,220
Do I need to

698
00:28:09,220 --> 00:28:11,100
check with you first?

699
00:28:11,980 --> 00:28:12,620
What

700
00:28:14,980 --> 00:28:16,060
are you planning to do here?

701
00:28:17,220 --> 00:28:17,940
What are you trying to say?

702
00:28:18,460 --> 00:28:19,460
I said

703
00:28:20,980 --> 00:28:22,700
all I needed to say twelve years ago.

704
00:28:23,820 --> 00:28:24,820
But

705
00:28:27,220 --> 00:28:28,860
I'm not sure you understood me clearly.

706
00:28:29,460 --> 00:28:30,740
You made yourself perfectly clear.

707
00:28:31,940 --> 00:28:33,100
No need to waste your breath.

708
00:28:33,500 --> 00:28:34,660
If there's nothing else,

709
00:28:35,340 --> 00:28:36,140
I have another class to teach.

710
00:28:36,460 --> 00:28:37,100
I'm leaving.

711
00:28:37,580 --> 00:28:38,180
Wait.

712
00:28:40,180 --> 00:28:41,140
You've seen it yourself.

713
00:28:41,940 --> 00:28:42,740
Rui

714
00:28:43,460 --> 00:28:45,020
has found his partner.

715
00:28:46,100 --> 00:28:47,700
They're very happy together.

716
00:28:48,660 --> 00:28:49,700
Before I came,

717
00:28:50,820 --> 00:28:52,820
I asked for his opinion.

718
00:28:54,220 --> 00:28:55,140
He said

719
00:28:57,020 --> 00:28:58,740
he never wants to see you again.

720
00:28:59,820 --> 00:29:00,660
What's past

721
00:29:02,380 --> 00:29:03,700
is past.

722
00:29:06,100 --> 00:29:06,900
So

723
00:29:09,100 --> 00:29:10,900
I hope you'll stop bothering him.

724
00:29:12,380 --> 00:29:14,220
Is this just you being presumptuous?

725
00:29:15,580 --> 00:29:17,780
I have no interest in anyone or anything

726
00:29:18,100 --> 00:29:19,020
related to your family.

727
00:29:20,220 --> 00:29:20,940
I just happened to

728
00:29:20,940 --> 00:29:23,260
bump into your daughter-in-law
at the training center.

729
00:29:23,780 --> 00:29:25,740
And I won't be going there.

730
00:29:26,660 --> 00:29:27,260
Good.

731
00:29:28,780 --> 00:29:30,420
I hope you'll keep your word.

732
00:29:33,620 --> 00:29:35,220
If it's about money,

733
00:29:36,540 --> 00:29:37,620
you don't need to go to such lengths.

734
00:29:37,900 --> 00:29:38,700
You could have

735
00:29:39,860 --> 00:29:40,620
come to me.

736
00:29:42,100 --> 00:29:42,980
You really haven't changed.

737
00:29:44,140 --> 00:29:45,580
After all these years,
you're still the same.

738
00:29:46,740 --> 00:29:48,580
Thinking that money
can solve everything.

739
00:29:49,620 --> 00:29:50,260
Thanks.

740
00:29:51,300 --> 00:29:52,020
But I don't need your money.

741
00:30:29,020 --> 00:30:29,820
There's

742
00:30:31,460 --> 00:30:32,700
500,000 in here.

743
00:30:35,540 --> 00:30:36,340
I want you

744
00:30:37,620 --> 00:30:38,700
to leave Rui.

745
00:30:43,340 --> 00:30:44,060
Gao Hui,

746
00:30:45,460 --> 00:30:47,140
you must've been waiting
a long time for this.

747
00:30:50,900 --> 00:30:52,860
You deliberately sent Feng Rui away,

748
00:30:53,780 --> 00:30:55,460
made sure I had the baby,

749
00:30:57,100 --> 00:30:58,780
and then kept us from seeing each other.

750
00:31:01,740 --> 00:31:02,900
The more you think that,

751
00:31:03,660 --> 00:31:05,860
the more I have to tell Feng Rui
what happened!

752
00:31:06,540 --> 00:31:07,940
I will wait for him to come back!

753
00:31:09,420 --> 00:31:10,580
I'll tell him myself

754
00:31:10,580 --> 00:31:11,860
that we lost our baby.

755
00:31:13,420 --> 00:31:14,860
I want him to see

756
00:31:15,220 --> 00:31:16,260
what his wonderful mother

757
00:31:16,260 --> 00:31:17,780
has done.

758
00:31:23,820 --> 00:31:25,020
You can tell him,

759
00:31:27,780 --> 00:31:28,380
but

760
00:31:30,340 --> 00:31:31,580
have you considered

761
00:31:33,500 --> 00:31:35,300
that my brother Haotian and your father

762
00:31:36,100 --> 00:31:38,100
will always be a barrier between us?

763
00:31:40,340 --> 00:31:41,420
Even if

764
00:31:41,660 --> 00:31:42,700
you stay together

765
00:31:43,220 --> 00:31:43,820
for a year,

766
00:31:43,940 --> 00:31:45,660
two years, or even three,

767
00:31:46,340 --> 00:31:47,220
one day,

768
00:31:48,340 --> 00:31:50,140
one of their names will come up.

769
00:31:50,860 --> 00:31:51,780
And when it does,

770
00:31:52,460 --> 00:31:53,700
you'll argue,

771
00:31:53,900 --> 00:31:54,340
fight,

772
00:31:54,820 --> 00:31:56,380
and even hurt each other,

773
00:31:57,020 --> 00:31:59,420
until all the love and respect

774
00:31:59,940 --> 00:32:00,860
are gone.

775
00:32:01,340 --> 00:32:02,540
Is that what you want?

776
00:32:03,020 --> 00:32:04,100
Do you really want to end up

777
00:32:04,540 --> 00:32:05,620
tearing each other apart,

778
00:32:07,260 --> 00:32:08,820
never speaking again?

779
00:32:10,460 --> 00:32:11,660
It'd be better

780
00:32:13,020 --> 00:32:13,660
for both of you

781
00:32:14,620 --> 00:32:16,260
to focus on your careers now.

782
00:32:17,900 --> 00:32:19,740
I think that's the best choice.

783
00:33:03,300 --> 00:33:03,820
Maybe

784
00:33:04,300 --> 00:33:05,660
we should just be together.

785
00:33:12,060 --> 00:33:13,060
Why bring this up all of a sudden?

786
00:33:15,660 --> 00:33:16,940
I just feel like

787
00:33:17,500 --> 00:33:19,340
we're already like a family now.

788
00:33:20,540 --> 00:33:21,620
I pick up Lexuan from school,

789
00:33:21,700 --> 00:33:22,940
teach him piano,

790
00:33:23,300 --> 00:33:24,300
cook for both of you, and...

791
00:33:24,740 --> 00:33:25,340
Okay.

792
00:33:29,740 --> 00:33:30,380
What did you say?

793
00:33:32,100 --> 00:33:32,660
I said

794
00:33:32,980 --> 00:33:33,380
okay.

795
00:33:37,060 --> 00:33:37,940
Are you serious?

796
00:33:38,820 --> 00:33:39,260
Of course.

797
00:33:40,340 --> 00:33:41,660
Aren't you serious?

798
00:33:46,180 --> 00:33:47,700
Of... Of course I am.

799
00:33:51,420 --> 00:33:52,380
Then it's settled?

800
00:33:54,820 --> 00:33:55,180
Okay.

801
00:33:55,820 --> 00:33:56,260
Settled.

802
00:34:11,700 --> 00:34:12,180
Well,

803
00:34:12,780 --> 00:34:13,420
I should get going now.

804
00:34:14,620 --> 00:34:14,980
Good night.

805
00:34:16,380 --> 00:34:16,820
Good night.

806
00:34:22,460 --> 00:34:22,860
Bye.

807
00:35:01,720 --> 00:35:07,340
♪An old dream is like
a sheet of pure white at hand♪

808
00:35:09,060 --> 00:35:14,500
♪Crumpled when held tight,
gone when you expand♪

809
00:35:16,260 --> 00:35:21,740
♪Silently, slowly, I begin to wake♪

810
00:35:22,300 --> 00:35:29,420
♪Occasional accidents sink
in someone's emotions?♪

811
00:35:30,140 --> 00:35:36,260
♪Who hasn't wondered if their life
would stay blank and bare?♪

812
00:35:37,220 --> 00:35:43,020
♪Acting on impulse,
believing futures fair♪

813
00:35:44,220 --> 00:35:49,780
♪Don't ask how to bury
faults of the past♪

814
00:35:51,980 --> 00:36:01,300
♪All my waiting is to make
the colors of encounters last♪

815
00:36:07,260 --> 00:36:09,860
♪This posture of steadfast faith♪

816
00:36:10,820 --> 00:36:13,900
♪Can't hide the weathering
of wind and rain's wraith♪

817
00:36:14,340 --> 00:36:17,340
♪Let the story settle
in the sea of faces♪

818
00:36:17,580 --> 00:36:21,380
♪Only then can the epilogue
leave its traces♪

819
00:36:21,700 --> 00:36:24,340
♪All those heavy loads we bore♪

820
00:36:24,980 --> 00:36:27,900
♪Were just time being generous,
nothing more♪

821
00:36:28,420 --> 00:36:31,500
♪If we look back,
a lingering warmth stays♪

822
00:36:31,740 --> 00:36:38,660
♪In the dialogue
where time and space part ways♪

823
00:37:35,420 --> 00:37:35,940
Coming.

824
00:37:39,940 --> 00:37:40,140
Rui.

825
00:37:40,140 --> 00:37:40,500
Where's my mom?

826
00:37:41,140 --> 00:37:41,620
On the second floor.

827
00:37:52,180 --> 00:37:52,780
Rui?

828
00:37:53,420 --> 00:37:54,020
You're back.

829
00:37:54,700 --> 00:37:55,820
Come here.

830
00:37:56,620 --> 00:37:57,060
Come on.

831
00:38:01,500 --> 00:38:02,940
Look at this little cutie.

832
00:38:05,020 --> 00:38:06,100
Little cutie.

833
00:38:06,860 --> 00:38:07,660
Look

834
00:38:08,460 --> 00:38:09,580
who's back.

835
00:38:11,140 --> 00:38:12,460
Daddy's back.

836
00:38:15,540 --> 00:38:15,980
Look.

837
00:38:19,900 --> 00:38:20,620
Where's Tan Siting?

838
00:38:23,060 --> 00:38:23,980
Isn't he adorable?

839
00:38:25,420 --> 00:38:25,860
Mom.

840
00:38:26,900 --> 00:38:28,540
The moment you get back,
you ask about her.

841
00:38:29,220 --> 00:38:31,100
Don't you care
about anyone else in the family?

842
00:38:36,300 --> 00:38:37,500
She left for France

843
00:38:38,180 --> 00:38:39,500
right after the baby was born.

844
00:38:41,740 --> 00:38:43,140
She said she couldn't give up ballet.

845
00:38:44,380 --> 00:38:45,820
It was her lifelong dream.

846
00:38:47,940 --> 00:38:48,420
Impossible.

847
00:38:49,860 --> 00:38:50,900
Siting isn't that kind of person.

848
00:38:51,980 --> 00:38:53,260
Artists think differently

849
00:38:54,140 --> 00:38:55,900
from the rest of us.

850
00:38:55,900 --> 00:38:57,300
♪Set off now,
facing the red dusk's glow♪

851
00:38:57,300 --> 00:38:58,260
After having a child,

852
00:38:59,340 --> 00:39:00,460
could she still dance?

853
00:39:00,460 --> 00:39:01,860
[Tan Siting]

854
00:39:01,860 --> 00:39:03,340
Don't be so naive.

855
00:39:03,340 --> 00:39:07,180
♪Turning your back
on the collapsed eaves below♪

856
00:39:11,220 --> 00:39:15,380
♪Wanting to reach
that far-off horizon's line♪

857
00:39:17,020 --> 00:39:24,060
♪So there's no time to stop♪

858
00:39:27,980 --> 00:39:32,100
♪Many things aren't
as complex as they seem♪

859
00:39:36,580 --> 00:39:40,780
♪I too have the right
to question and dream♪

860
00:39:44,900 --> 00:39:49,420
♪What we've seen or missed
are but moments fleet♪

861
00:39:51,100 --> 00:39:57,620
♪Just like the different flowers
in dreams I meet♪

862
00:39:58,980 --> 00:40:02,220
♪Where should I place
my love and heart?♪

863
00:40:02,220 --> 00:40:03,580
I never believed

864
00:40:04,740 --> 00:40:05,900
you'd abandon me and Lexuan

865
00:40:05,900 --> 00:40:07,180
for ballet.

866
00:40:07,220 --> 00:40:08,700
♪What price must I pay?♪

867
00:40:08,700 --> 00:40:09,660
Not until I saw with my own eyes

